;About Firefox for Android
有關 Firefox for Android


;<dt>Who makes Firefox?</dt> <dd>Mozilla is a global, nonprofit organization dedicated to making the Web better. We emphasize principle over profit, and believe that the Web is a shared public resource to be cared for, not a commodity to be sold. We work with a worldwide community to create open source products like Mozilla Firefox, and to innovate for the benefit of the individual and the betterment of the Web. The result is great products built by passionate people and better choices for everyone.</dd>
<dt>誰創造了 Firefox？</dt> <dd>全球性非營利組織 Mozilla 致力打造 Web 的美好未來。我們堅守自己的理念，另外相信 Web 應該是開放並易於取用的全球公用資源，而非用以販售牟利的商品。Mozilla 與全球社群通力合作，打造如 Mozilla Firefox 的開放源碼產品，並為個人與 Web 的福祉持續引領創新，將熱心人士所建構的絕佳產品提供予所有人。</dd>


;<dt>How is Firefox for Android different from other mobile browsers?</dt> <dd>Firefox for Android is built on the same technology platform as Firefox for the desktop, making it fast, easy to use and secure. Firefox also uses Sync technology to bring your desktop history, bookmarks, passwords and form data to your mobile devices. Firefox for Android is the only mobile browser that offers user-centric, innovative features while still fiercely safeguarding your privacy and data, for instance with <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/how-do-i-turn-do-not-track-feature-mobile">Do Not Track</a>.</dd>
<dt>Firefox for Android 何以與其他行動瀏覽器有所不同？</dt> <dd>Firefox for Android 植基於 Firefox 桌面版的相同技術平台，也因此更快、更安全、更簡單易用。Firefox 另具備 Sync 技術，可將桌面版的密碼、書籤、瀏覽記錄都同步到你的行動裝置上。Firefox for Android 並是唯一以使用者為中心而提供創新功能的行動瀏覽器，且透過如<a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/how-do-i-turn-do-not-track-feature-mobile">不要追蹤我 (Do Not Track)</a> 的功能，確實保護你的隱私與資料。</dd>


;<dt>Is Firefox available for my platform or device?</dt> <dd>Firefox for Android works with Android phones version 2.2 (Froyo) and above. <a href="/firefox/mobile/platforms">Visit our list of supported platforms and devices</a>.</dd>
<dt>Firefox 可用於哪些平台或裝置？</dt> <dd>Firefox for Android 可用於 Android 2.2 (Froyo) 或更高版本的裝置。<a href="/firefox/mobile/platforms">請參閱目前支援平台與裝置的清單</a>。</dd>


;<dt>Is Firefox available in my language?</dt> <dd>Firefox is currently available in more than 10 languages and we're working on adding more. Check the <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.mozilla.firefox">Google Play Store</a> to see if yours is supported.</dd>
<dt>Firefox 是否提供我熟悉的語言版本？</dt> <dd>Firefox 目前提供超過 10 種語言版本，而我們也持續努力提供更多語言。可至 <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.mozilla.firefox">Google Play Store</a> 查看目前是否支援你的語言。</dd>


;<dt>Does Firefox for Android support Flash content?</dt> <dd>Yes, Firefox for Android supports Flash on phones with Android version 2.2 and above.</dd>
<dt>Firefox for Android 支援 Flash 嗎？</dt> <dd>當然，只要裝置搭載 Android 2.2 或更高版本，Firefox for Android 均可支援 Flash。</dd>


