;<dt>Why do some websites not display properly?</dt> <dd>While we continue to make small modifications to improve the browser experience, our team and thousands of volunteer contributors around the world are working to help sites make the small adjustments necessary to support our implementation of open standards so that all Web pages render beautifully. We are confident these efforts will be successful, just as they were when Firefox Desktop initially entered the market.</dd>
<dt>為何無法正確顯示某些網站？</dt> <dd>我們不斷修改相關細節，以提升瀏覽器使用經驗。Mozilla 團隊再加上全球數千名的志工，都熱心協助網站進行微調，以完整支援我們所建構的開放標準，進而呈現更賞心悅目的網頁。我們相信這些努力不會白費，就如同 Firefox 桌面版一樣成功。</dd>


;<dt>How do I use the start page?</dt> <dd>Your personalized start page helps you get to your favorite parts of the Web effortlessly with easily accessible thumbnail links to your top sites and tabs from your last browsing session.</dd>
<dt>我要如何使用開始頁面？</dt> <dd>可個人化的開始頁面，會根據你最近的瀏覽記錄，將你最常瀏覽的網站設為縮圖鏈結，協助你輕鬆找到網頁中自己最喜愛的部份。</dd>


;<dt>What does the Awesome Screen do? <dd>The Awesome Screen gets you to where you want to go quickly with less typing by giving you a list of your most often visited sites along with the ability to browse through your bookmarks, history and open tabs from across your devices. <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/use-awesome-screen-search-firefox-android">Learn more</a>.</dd>
<dt>智慧畫面 (Awesome Screen) 的功能為何？<dd>現在你只要輸入幾個字母，智慧畫面就會提供你最常瀏覽網站的清單，並能跨裝置找到你的書籤、瀏覽記錄、已開啟的分頁，讓你能更迅速瀏覽網站。<a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/use-awesome-screen-search-firefox-android">進一步了解</a>。</dd>


;<dt>What is Firefox Sync?</dt> <dd>Firefox Sync brings your desktop data to all your devices so you can securely access your history, bookmarks, tabs and passwords from anywhere. <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/how-do-i-set-up-firefox-sync">Learn how to set up Sync</a>.</dd>

<dt>Firefox Sync 的功能為何？</dt> <dd>Firefox Sync 可將你的桌面板資料同步到其他裝置，讓你在任何地點都能安全存取自己的書籤、密碼、分頁、瀏覽記錄。<a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/how-do-i-set-up-firefox-sync">了解該如何設定 Sync 同步功能</a>。</dd>


;<dt>What are add-ons and how can I get them?</dt> <dd>Add-ons let you customize the look, features and functionality of Firefox. <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/getting-started-firefox-mobile#w_how-do-i-find-and-install-add-ons">Find out how to add them to your Firefox</a>.</dd>
<dt>什麼是附加元件，又該如何取得？</dt> <dd>附加元件可讓你客製 Firefox 的外觀、特色、功能。<a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/getting-started-firefox-mobile#w_how-do-i-find-and-install-add-ons">了解 Firefox 安裝附加元件的方法</a>。</dd>


;Privacy and Security
隱私與安全


;<dt>How will Firefox keep me safe while I browse?</dt> <dd>Mozilla was the first to implement the Do No Track privacy feature. Firefox also features customizable security settings to manage passwords, history, private data, cookies, site options and add-ons. <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/configure-mobile-privacy-and-security-settings">Learn more</a>.</dd>
<dt>Firefox 要如何保障我的瀏覽安全？</dt> <dd>Mozilla 率先建構了「不要追蹤我 (Do No Track)」隱私功能。Firefox 亦提供可客製化的安全設定，讓你能管理 cookies、密碼、瀏覽記錄、隱私資料、網站選項、附加元件。<a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/configure-mobile-privacy-and-security-settings">進一步了解</a>。</dd>


;<dt>What is Do Not Track?</dt> <dd>Firefox for Android is the first mobile browser to offer the Do Not Track privacy feature to give you more control over the way your online behavior is tracked and used. Do Not Track lets you tell websites that you want to opt out of behavioral tracking. Learn how to turn it on <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/how-do-i-turn-do-not-track-feature">for desktop</a> and <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/how-do-i-turn-do-not-track-feature-mobile">for mobile</a>.</dd>
<dt>什麼是「不要追蹤我 (DNT)」？</dt> <dd>Firefox for Android 是第一款提供「不要追蹤我」隱私功能的行動瀏覽器，可讓你掌控自己線上行為受到追蹤與使用的情況。DNT 將幫你拒絕網站對你的行為追蹤作業。進一步了解應如何開啟<a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/how-do-i-turn-do-not-track-feature">桌面版</a>與<a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/how-do-i-turn-do-not-track-feature-mobile">行動版</a>的 DNT 功能。</dd>


;<dt>What is Master Password and how do I use it?</dt> <dd>The Master Password protects usernames and passwords that you save in Firefox. <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/use-master-password-protect-passwords-firefox-andr">Learn how to enable this feature</a>.</dd>
<dt>什麼是主控密碼？又該如何使用？</dt> <dd>主控密碼 (Master Password) 可保護你儲存在 Firefox 中的使用者名稱與密碼。<a href="https://support.mozilla.org/kb/use-master-password-protect-passwords-firefox-andr">進一步啟用此功能</a>。</dd>


